<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Namma Chennai - Explore the Beauty</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* --- RESET & VARIABLES --- */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff9933; /* Kept your project's orange */
            --primary-dark: #e68a00;
            --text-dark: #333;
            --text-light: #666;
            --white: #fff;
            --dark-overlay: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        a { text-decoration: none; }

        /* --- NAVIGATION --- */
        nav {
            background: #2c3e50; /* Dark Blue like reference */
            padding: 15px 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .logo {
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .logo span { color: var(--primary-color); }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary-color); }

        .btn-login {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            color: white !important;
            transition: background 0.3s !important;
        }

        .btn-login:hover { background: var(--primary-dark) !important; }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            /* Using one of your images as background */
            background: linear-gradient(var(--dark-overlay), var(--dark-overlay)), url('/static/images/san2.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--white);
            padding-top: 60px;
        }

        .hero h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px 0 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 153, 51, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .hero-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            background: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        /* --- ABOUT SECTION --- */
        .about {
            padding: 80px 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 50px;
            background: white;
            min-height: 80vh; /* Ensures it takes up space */
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 500px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* The stylistic border frame from your reference */
        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 10px solid #fff; 
            outline: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .about-content {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .about-subtitle {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: block;
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        }

        .about-content p {
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: "‚ûú";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 15px 20px; }
            .nav-links { display: none; } /* Hide nav on mobile for simplicity */
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .about { flex-direction: column; padding: 50px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">üìç Namma <span>Chennai</span></div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="/login_page" class="btn-login">Login / Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h3>Welcome To South India</h3>
        <h1>Namma Chennai</h1>
        <p>Explore the beauty of Chennai, from historic temples to the breezy Marina beach. Your ultimate guide to the Gateway of South India.</p>
        <a href="#about" class="hero-btn">Discover Now</a>
    </header>

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="about-image">
            <img src="/static/images/Media (1).jpg" alt="About Chennai">
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <span class="about-subtitle">About Us</span>
            <h2>Welcome to Namma Chennai</h2>
            <p>
                Chennai, formerly Madras, is a city that perfectly blends the old with the new. 
                Whether you are a history buff, a foodie, or a beach lover, this city has something for everyone.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our project, "Explore Namma Chennai", aims to provide tourists and locals alike with a 
                curated list of must-visit spots, complete with historical facts, real-time weather updates, 
                and easy navigation.
            </p>
            
            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Historical Landmarks</li>
                <li>Real-time Weather</li>
                <li>Interactive Maps</li>
                <li>Hotel Recommendations</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>¬© 2026 Explore Namma Chennai. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
